.SH NAME
encspot \- guess encoder used to create MP3 files
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B encspot
.RI [\fIFILE\fR]...
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B encspot
For a given list of MP3 files encspot displays technical information and attempts to determine which encoder
was used to create them.
.PP
